Afropop singer Seyi Shay has disclosed she’s engaged. The “Ragga Ragga” singer, in a recent interview with Beat FM, spotting a diamond engagement ring, said: “Some guy gave it to me and said, ‘hey, would you marry me?’” When quizzed about her new glow, she admitted that her engagement to her undisclosed fiancée is a contributing factor as it further amplified her already existing glow.   Anita Joseph to marriage critics: you will sink first     2022 Grammy Awards rescheduled to April 3     Wizkid, Tiwa Savage, others battle for 2022 NAACP Awards   Read Also: Why I took five years to release sophomore album, by Seyi Shay “I was already glowing before I met the guy. So he just added to the glow. If there was no ribbon on the package, I would not have said yes,” she said. - Advertisement - There have also been rumours that she may be pregnant following a video she posted sometimes in December, 2021. Seyi Shay however declined to say anything about it when asked.